Actress and presenter Pearl Thusi hopes to win an Oscar at the awards next year. The South African actress who has made her mark internationally and starred in shows such as Quantico took to Twitter and expressed that it would be great if she could win an Oscar at the Academy Awards next year. The actress who has a proven track record as as reputable actress further encouraged people to dream big and told them their dreams are valid. ''What if I won an Oscar at the 100th Academy Awards… What if nje… asiphupheni ma-eh. Your dreams are valid yazi,'' she wrote. What if I won an Oscar at the 100th Academy Awards...What if nje... asiphupheni ma-eh.Your dreams are valid yazi.  